segments.text:
For that day is of the Lord, Yahweh of Armies, a day of vengeance, 
that he may avenge himself of his adversaries. The sword will devour and be satiated, and will drink its fill of their blood; 
for the Lord, Yahweh of Armies, has a sacrifice in the north country by the river Euphrates.

The nations have heard of your shame, and the earth is full of your cry; 
for the mighty man has stumbled against the mighty, 
they both fall together.

for I am with you; 
for I will make a full end of all the nations where I have driven you, but I will not make a full end of you, but I will correct you in measure, 
and will in no way leave you unpunished.
